              <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;">
                <span id="step3TypeSummary" style="color:#F8F2E6;font-size:0.85rem;">Baby Book</span>
                <span id="step3PriceSummary" style="color:#B8935A;font-weight:700;font-size:0.85rem;">$29 first year</span>
